⊢ seed-topic
  given question ≡ "What are the key challenges in quantum error correction?"
  yield summary, follow-ups[]

  ∴ Research «question». Write a 2-sentence «summary».
    Identify 3 specific follow-up questions as «follow-ups».

  ⊨ summary is 2-3 sentences
  ⊨ follow-ups has exactly 3 items
  ⊨ each follow-up is a question (ends with ?)

⊢⊢ explore
  given seed-topic→follow-ups
  given §seed-topic
  yield §new-cells[]
  until depth > 2 ∨ follow-ups all empty
  max 9

  ∴ For each follow-up in «seed-topic→follow-ups», create a new cell
    modeled on «§seed-topic» but with that follow-up as its question.
    Each spawned cell also yields follow-ups, feeding the next depth level.

  ⊨ §new-cells[] each have same given/yield signature as «§seed-topic»
  ⊨ total spawned cells ≤ 9

⊢ synthesis
  given explore→§new-cells
  yield report

  ∴ Collect all summaries from the spawned cells.
    Write a comprehensive «report» synthesizing all findings.

  ⊨ report references findings from at least 3 spawned cells
